<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Enin, Luikhuk thuk leh lien chuh,
 Enin, a luong zing hi;
 Hukdampa naka put ahi,
 Vuk banga thienna chuh (2)

[V2]
 Lui a chun hungin,
 Tun le a luong zing;
 A nuom cheng manbei a hungin,
 Gitloh silthieng u-nau.

[V3]
 2. Lungngai, gima Isu thawkna,
 Kalvari kross apat;
 Thisan maktak a hung luong dawk,
 Vuk bang a thienna chu (2)

[V4]
 3. Zie lui hihdam theihna mak chuh,
 I bawnun he leu hing;
 Thisan lun mai chuh gingchai tiu,
 Vuk banga thienna chuh (2)

[V5]
 4. A tawpleh zie a chu chieh ding-
 A sap I hih tieng leh;
 I ginuh thisan hizing ding,
 Vuk banga thienna chu (2)</lyrics>
<title>THE CLEASING FOUNTAIN</title>
<hymn_number>101</hymn_number>
</song>